languages.text: "Приступим же к трапезе. Не бойся, мон-кай, ты умрешь нескоро. Я планирую растянуть удовольствие".
"Let us feast, then. Don't be scared, mon-keigh, you won't die too soon. I intend to savour every moment."
languages.original_text: "Приступим же к трапезе. Не бойся, мон-кай, ты умрешь нескоро. Я планирую растянуть удовольствие".

languages.text: « Festoyons, dans ce cas. N'ayez pas peur, mon-keigh, vous ne mourrez pas de suite. J'ai bien l'intention de savourer chaque instant. »
languages.original_text: "Let us feast, then. Don't be scared, mon-keigh, you won't die too soon. I intend to savour every moment."

traits.locale_text: « Festoyons, dans ce cas. N'ayez pas peur, mon-keigh, vous ne mourrez pas de suite. J'ai bien l'intention de savourer chaque instant. »
traits.speaker: DrukhariLeaderM

languages.text: “那咱们就来饱餐一顿吧。不用怕，猴子，你不会死得太快。我打算好好享受每一刻。”
languages.original_text: "Let us feast, then. Don't be scared, mon-keigh, you won't die too soon. I intend to savour every moment."

traits.locale_text: “那咱们就来饱餐一顿吧。不用怕，猴子，你不会死得太快。我打算好好享受每一刻。”
traits.speaker: DrukhariLeaderM

languages.text: 「では頂くとしよう。怖がるな、モン＝ケイよ。すぐに死ぬことはない。じっくりと味わうつもりだからな」
languages.original_text: "Let us feast, then. Don't be scared, mon-keigh, you won't die too soon. I intend to savour every moment."

traits.locale_text: 「では頂くとしよう。怖がるな、モン＝ケイよ。すぐに死ぬことはない。じっくりと味わうつもりだからな」
traits.speaker: DrukhariLeaderM

languages.text: "Lasst uns also ein Fest feiern. Aber keine Sorge, Chem-Pan-Sey, so schnell werdet Ihr nicht sterben. Ich werde jeden Moment davon auskosten."
languages.original_text: "Let us feast, then. Don't be scared, mon-keigh, you won't die too soon. I intend to savour every moment."

traits.locale_text: "Lasst uns also ein Fest feiern. Aber keine Sorge, Chem-Pan-Sey, so schnell werdet Ihr nicht sterben. Ich werde jeden Moment davon auskosten."
traits.speaker: DrukhariLeaderM

languages.text: «Procedamos con el festín, pues. No temas, mon-keigh, no morirás enseguida. Pretendo saborear cada instante».
languages.original_text: "Let us feast, then. Don't be scared, mon-keigh, you won't die too soon. I intend to savour every moment."

traits.locale_text: «Procedamos con el festín, pues. No temas, mon-keigh, no morirás enseguida. Pretendo saborear cada instante».
traits.speaker: DrukhariLeaderM

languages.text: "O hâlde ziyafet başlasın. Hiç korkma mon-keigh, hemen ölmeyeceksin. Her anın tadını doyasıya çıkarmak niyetindeyim."
